Title: Add option for number of items to show in topics
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: multisite
Date: 1614160944
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

You have now the option to set the number of items that should be shown in
topics until the "Show all" option is painted. All remaining items will only be
visible, if the "Show all" option is used.

This option can be found on creating or editing topics.
